In your toggle method you need to set `this.isActive` to `null` if the same item is clicked again.

```
methods: {
  toggleItem(index) {
    this.isActive = this.isActive === index ? null : index;
  },
}
```

FYI, there is an extra double quotes (`&quot;`) after the `@click` on the `li`.

Refactor `toggleItem` to:

```js
toggleItem(index) {
  this.isActive = (this.isActive === index) ? null : index;
}
```

This will set `isActive` to null if `index` matches `isActive`, otherwise set `isActive` to `index`.

